data.description: Beautifully updated two-family home located in the Village of Tuckahoe. Full gut renovation First floor unit consists of updated kitchen, living room, two bedrooms and full bath, large front patio. Second floor (Duplex) unit consists of updated kitchen dining room, living room, 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, backyard space and deck. Basement offers laundry room and storage. Short distance to train station, restaurants and shops, and a perfect location. Great opportunity for investors!!! *Information believed true but not warranted*
